title: The End of ‘Game of Thrones’ Is Near, Plus: ‘Survivor’ Season Finale | The Watch
description:
‘Game of Thrones’ is over this Sunday (1:00). We look back at the penultimate episode (7:40), make some predictions for the finale (20:32), and speculate about what a Benioff and Weiss ‘Star Wars’ movie will look like (26:32). Plus, the ‘Survivor’ season finale (42:12).

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald
Guest: Riley McAtee
